data.name: label1.Text
data.value: The storage room reeked of an awful, stomach turning scent of rot. You stumble upon a large mass of several animal carcasses piled on top of each other. They seem to be rotting for quite some time now and you're sure of that fact because worms and flies are swarming over them. Horrified by the grotesque sight, you ran back to the town hall to seek refuge.
